This folder contains scripts that add new commands to GDB. These new commands enhanced support for debugging HPX applications.
To add these commands to GDB append the following lines to '.gdbinit' file in your home directory.

directory ~/git-repos/hpx/scripts/gdb
source hpx_prefix_cmd.py
source print_var.py

Commands List:
hpx print

Use the 'help' command to learn about the usage for these commands.
